\c 25
\s Umnyaka wesabatha lowejubili
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi entabeni yeSinayi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Nxa lifika elizweni engilinika lona, ilizwe lizaphumula, isabatha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 23.10,11. 26.34,35. 2 Lan. 36.21.\x*.
\v 3 Iminyaka eyisithupha uzahlanyela insimu yakho, leminyaka eyisithupha uthene isivini sakho, ubuthe isithelo saso.
\v 4 Kodwa ngomnyaka wesikhombisa kuzakuba lesabatha lokuphumula kwelizwe, isabatha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Kawuyikuhlanyela insimu yakho, ungatheni isivini sakho\x + 25.11. 2 Kho. 19.29. Isa. 37.30.\x*.
\v 5 Kawuyikuvuna umkhukhuzela wesivuno sakho, kaliyikukha izithelo zamavini akho angathenwanga. Uzakuba ngumnyaka wokuphumula welizwe.
\v 6 Njalo isabatha lelizwe lizakuba yikudla kwenu, ngokwakho, lokwenceku yakho, lokwencekukazi yakho, lokoqhatshiweyo wakho, lokowemzini wakho ohlala lawe njengowezizwe,
\v 7 lokwezifuyo zakho, lokwenyamazana eziselizweni lakho; konke elikuthelayo kuzakuba yikudla.
\p
\v 8 Uzazibalela-ke amaviki ayisikhombisa eminyaka, iminyaka eyisikhombisa ephindwe kasikhombisa, ukuze insuku zamaviki ayisikhombisa eminyaka zibe yiminyaka engamatshumi amane lesificamunwemunye kuwe.
\v 9 Khona uzadlulisa uphondo lomsindo omkhulu enyangeni yesikhombisa ngolwetshumi lwenyanga; ngosuku lwenhlawulo yokuthula lizadlulisa \add umsindo\add* wophondo elizweni lonke lakini\x + 23.24,27.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo lizangcwelisa lumnyaka wamatshumi amahlanu, limemezele inkululeko elizweni kubo bonke abakhileyo balo. Kuzakuba \w lijubili\w** kini\x + Isa. 61.1. Jer. 34.8,15,17. Hez. 46.17. Isa. 61.2. 63.4. Luka 4.19.\x*; lizabuyela, ngulowo lalowo, elifeni lakhe; futhi lizabuyela, ngulowo lalowo, kusapho lwakhe\x + 25.13. 27.24. Nani 36.4.\x*.
\v 11 Umnyaka wamatshumi amahlanu uzakuba ngumnyaka wejubili kini; lingahlanyeli, lingavuni umkhukhuzela wawo\x + 25.5.\x*, lingakhi ngawo ku\add mavini\add* angathenwanga\x + 25.5.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba ulijubili, uzakuba ngcwele kini; lizakudla ensimini okuthelwayo kwayo\x + 25.6,7.\x*.
\v 13 Ngomnyaka walelijubili lizabuyela, ngulowo lalowo elifeni lakhe\x + 25.10.\x*.
\v 14 Uba-ke uthengisa ulutho kumakhelwane wakho loba uthenga esandleni sikamakhelwane wakho, lingacindezelani\x + 25.17; 19.33.\x*.
\v 15 Ngokwenani leminyaka emva kwejubili uzathenga kumakhelwane wakho; ngokwenani leminyaka yokuthelwayo uzakuthengisela\x + 27.18,23.\x*.
\v 16 Ngobunengi beminyaka uzakwandisa intengo yakho; njalo ngobulutshwana beminyaka uzanciphisa intengo yakho; ngoba ekuthengisela inani lezivuno.
\v 17 Ngakho lingacindezelani\x + 25.14.\x*, kodwa wesabe uNkulunkulu wakho. Ngoba ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 25.36,43; 19.14,32.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ngakho yenzani izimiso zami, ligcine izehlulelo zami, lizenze\x + 18.4,5.\x*, ukuze lihlale elizweni livikelekile\x + 25.19; 26.5. Dute. 12.10. Hlab. 4.8. Hez. 34.25,28. Jobe 11.18. Zaga 1.33. Jer. 23.6.\x*.
\v 19 Lelizwe lizathela izithelo zalo, lidle lize lisuthe, lihlale kulo livikelekile\x + 26.5. Dute. 11.15. Jow. 2.19,26.\x*.
\v 20 Uba-ke lisithi: Sizakudlani ngomnyaka wesikhombisa?\x + Mat. 6.25,31.\x* Khangela, kasihlanyeli, kasibuthi isivuno sethu\x + 25.4,5.\x*.
\v 21 Khona ngizalaya isibusiso sami kini ngomnyaka wesithupha, ukuze uthele isivuno seminyaka emithathu\x + Eks. 16.29.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo lizahlanyela ngomnyaka wesificaminwembili lidle\x + 2 Kho. 19.29.\x* okwesivuno esidala kuze kufike umnyaka wesificamunwemunye; kuze kufike isivuno sawo lizakudla esidala\x + Josh. 5.11,12. Levi 26.10.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Lelizwe kaliyikuthengiswa lanininini, ngoba ilizwe ngelami\x + Dute. 32.43. 2 Lan. 7.20. Hlab. 85.1. Jow. 2.18; 3.2.\x*; ngoba lingabemzini labahlala njengabezizwe lami\x + 1 Lan. 29.15. Hlab. 39.12; 119.19. Heb. 11.13. 1 Pet. 1.17; 2.11.\x*.
\v 24 Lelizweni lonke lelifa lenu lizavumela uhlengo lwelizwe.
\p
\v 25 Uba umfowenu esiba ngumyanga, athengise okwelifa lakhe, uzafika\x + Ruthe 2.20; 4.4,6.\x* umhlengi wakhe eyisihlobo sakhe, ahlenge lokho umfowabo akuthengisileyo\x + Ruthe 3.9,12. Jer. 32.7,8.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo umuntu, uba engelaye umhlengi, kodwa isandla sakhe sifinyelele, athole okwenele uhlengo lwakhe,
\v 27 kabale iminyaka yokuthengiswa kwalo, abuyisele okuseleyo kulowomuntu owamthengisela lona, abuyele elifeni lakhe\x + 25.50,51,52.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa uba isandla sakhe singatholanga okwenele ukubuyisela kuye, okuthengisiweyo kuzakuba sesandleni sokuthengileyo kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili; kodwa ngejubili kuzaphuma, njalo uzabuyela elifeni lakhe.
\p
\v 29 Umuntu, uba ethengisa-ke indlu yokuhlala emzini olomthangala, ilungelo lohlengo lwayo lizakuba kuze kuphele umnyaka wokuthengiswa kwayo; ilungelo lohlengo lwayo lizakuba ngumnyaka wonke\x + 25.30. Gen. 24.55.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa uba ingahlengwanga uze umnyaka wayo wonke ugcwale, leyondlu esemzini olomthangala izamiselwa lowo owayithengayo njalonjalo, ezizukulwaneni zakhe; kayiyikuphuma ngejubili.
\v 31 Kodwa izindlu zemizi engabiyelwanga ngomthangala zizabalwa njengensimu yelizwe; kulohlengo lwayo, njalo izaphuma ngejubili.
\v 32 Mayelana lemizi yamaLevi, izindlu zemizi yelifa lawo, amaLevi azakuba lohlengo lwaphakade\x + Nani 35.2. Josh. 21.2,.\x*.
\v 33 Uba kungohlenga kumaLevi, kuzaphuma ukuthengiswa kwendlu lokomuzi welifa lakhe ngejubili; ngoba izindlu zemizi yamaLevi ziyilifa lawo phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 25.28,30,31,41,54; 27.21.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa insimu yamaphethelo emizi yawo kayiyikuthengiswa, ngoba iyilifa lawo kuze kube nininini\x + Nani 35.2. Josh. 21.11-42; 1 Lan. 6.55-81; 13.2. Seb. 4.36,37.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Uba-ke umfowenu esiba ngumyanga, lesandla sakhe sixega kuwe, uzamsekela: Owemzini lohlezi njengowezizwe, ukuze aphile lawe\x + Dute. 15.7,8. Hlab. 41.1; 112.5,9. Zaga 14.31. 1 Joha. 3.17.\x*.
\v 36 Ungathathi kuye umvuzo lenzuzo\x + Eks. 22.25.\x*, kodwa wesabe uNkulunkulu wakho, ukuze umfowenu aphile lawe\x + 25.17; Neh. 5.9.\x*.
\v 37 Ungamuphi imali yakho ngenzalo, futhi ungaphi ukudla kwakho ngenzuzo\x + 25.42,55; 22.33; 26.13.\x*.
\v 38 NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu owalikhupha elizweni leGibhithe ukulinika ilizwe leKhanani, ukuze ngibe nguNkulunkulu wenu.
\p
\v 39 Uba-ke umfowenu olawe esiba ngumyanga, azithengise kuwe, ungamenzi asebenze njengesigqili\x + Eks. 21.2. Dute. 15.12. 1 Kho. 9.22. 2 Kho. 4.1. Neh. 5.5. Jer. 34.14.\x*;
\v 40 uzakuba lawe njengoqhatshiweyo, njengohlala njengowezizwe, asebenze kuwe kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili.
\v 41 Khona ezaphuma kuwe, yena labantwana bakhe laye\x + Eks. 21.2,3.\x*, abuyele kwabomdeni wakhe, abuyele elifeni laboyise\x + 25.28.\x*.
\v 42 Ngoba ziyizinceku zami engazikhupha elizweni leGibhithe; kaziyikuthengiswa ngokuthengiswa kwesigqili\x + 25.55. Roma 6.22.\x*.
\v 43 Ungambusi nzima\x + Efe. 6.9. Kol. 4.1.\x*\x + 25.46,53. Eks. 1.13,14. Hez. 34. 4.\x*, kodwa wesabe uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 25.17. Mal. 3.5.\x*.
\v 44 Lesigqili sakho lesigqilikazi sakho ozakuba lazo, zizavela ezizweni ezilizingelezeleyo; kuzo lizathenga isigqili kumbe isigqilikazi.
\v 45 Futhi-ke ebantwaneni balabo abahlala njengabemzini abahlala njengabezizwe lani, kubo lingazithenga lakuzizukulwana zabo ezilani, abazizalela elizweni lakini, njalo bazakuba yimfuyo yenu.
\v 46 Njalo lizazenza abafuyi bazo \add lisenz\add*ela abantwana benu emva kwenu ukuze badle ilifa lemfuyo\x + Isa. 14.2.\x*; lizabasebenzisa kuze kube nininini. Kodwa phakathi kwabafowenu, abantwana bakoIsrayeli, kaliyikubusa nzima, omunye phezu komunye\x + 25.43.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Uba-ke isandla sowezizweni loba sowemzini ohlala lawe sesifinyelele \add enothweni\add*, lomfowenu olaye abe ngumyanga, azithengise kowemzini, owezizweni ohlala lawe, kumbe kusendo lwesizukulwana sowemzini\x + 25.25,35,39.\x*,
\v 48 esezithengisile kungaba lokuhlengwa kwakhe; omunye wabafowabo angamhlenga\x + Neh. 5.1-5.\x*,
\v 49 loba umfowabo kayise, loba umtanomfowabo kayise angamhlenga, kumbe isihlobo sakhe segazi emdeni wakhe singamhlenga\x + 18.6.\x*; uba isandla sakhe sesifinyelele \add enothweni\add*, angazihlenga\x + 25.26,47.\x*.
\v 50 Uzabalisana lowamthengayo, kusukela emnyakeni owazithengisa kuye ngawo kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili; ukuze imali yentengiso yakhe izakuba njengenani leminyaka, njengensuku zoqhatshiweyo kuzakuba njalo ngaye\x + Jobe 7.1. Isa. 16.14; 21.16.\x*.
\v 51 Uba kuseleminyaka eminengi, ngokungayo uzabuyisela uhlengo lwakhe, emalini yokuthengwa kwakhe\x + 25.16,52; 27.8.\x*.
\v 52 Uba-ke kusele iminyaka emilutshwana kuze kufike umnyaka wejubili, uzabalisana laye; njengokweminyaka yakhe uzabuyisela uhlengo lwakhe.
\v 53 Uzakuba laye njengoqhatshiweyo iminyaka ngeminyaka; kayikumbusa nzima phambi kwamehlo akho\x + 25.43.\x*.
\v 54 Kodwa uba engahlengwanga ngalokhu, uzaphuma ngomnyaka wejubili, yena labantwana bakhe kanye laye\x + 25.41. Eks. 21.2,3.\x*.
\v 55 Ngoba kimi abantwana bakoIsrayeli bazinceku, bazinceku zami engazikhupha elizweni leGibhithe\x + 25.42.\x*. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
